Here is a ready-to-use starter kit—a single HTML file that already looks polished and can be expanded later.  
Just copy it into a file called index.html, replace the three placeholder photos with your own, and upload the file (plus the images) to any free host (GitHub Pages, Netlify, Vercel, etc.). No build tools or frameworks are required.

```
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Intelligent Scholars Academy</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root{
      --primary:#ff6b6b;
      --secondary:#3742fa;
      --bg:#f7f9fc;
      --text:#2c3e50;
    }
    *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;color:var(--text)}
    body{background:var(--bg);line-height:1.6}
    header{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--primary),var(--secondary));color:#fff;padding:90px 20px 50px;text-align:center}
    header h1{font-size:2.8rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:.5rem}
    header p{font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:300}
    nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;width:100%;background:#fff;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.05);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:15px 30px;z-index:999}
    nav .logo{font-weight:600;font-size:1.2rem;color:var(--primary)}
    nav ul{list-style:none;display:flex;gap:20px}
    nav a{text-decoration:none;font-size:.95rem;transition:.3s}
    nav a:hover{color:var(--primary)}
    .container{max-width:1000px;margin:80px auto;padding:0 20px}
    section{margin-bottom:80px}
    h2{font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:25px;text-align:center;position:relative}
    h2::after{content:"";position:absolute;left:50%;bottom:-8px;width:50px;height:3px;background:var(--primary);transform:translateX(-50%)}
    .features{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:30px;text-align:center}
    .card{background:#fff;border-radius:12px;padding:30px 20px;box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,.05);transition:.3s}
    .card:hover{transform:translateY(-6px)}
    .card img{width:64px;margin-bottom:15px}
    .card h3{font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:10px;font-weight:600}
    footer{background:#2c3e50;color:#fff;text-align:center;padding:25px 0;font-size:.9rem}
    .cta{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--primary),var(--secondary));color:#fff;text-align:center;padding:60px 20px;border-radius:12px}
    .cta a{background:#fff;color:var(--secondary);padding:12px 30px;border-radius:50px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;margin-top:15px;display:inline-block;transition:.3s}
    .cta a:hover{background:#ececec}
    @media(max-width:600px){
      header h1{font-size:2.2rem}
      nav{flex-direction:column;padding:10px 15px}
      nav ul{gap:12px}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="logo">Intelligent Scholars</div>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<header>
  <h1>Intelligent Scholars Academy</h1>
  <p>Empowering the next generation with confidence, curiosity and clarity.</p>
</header>

<div class="container">
  <section id="about">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p style="text-align:center;max-width:700px;margin:auto">
      We are a youth orientation academy focused on leadership, academic excellence, and lifelong learning.  
      Through interactive workshops, mentorship and community projects, we help teenagers discover their strengths and shape their futures.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="features">
    <h2>What We Offer</h2>
    <div class="features">
      <div class="card">
        <img src="leadership.svg" alt="icon"/>
        <h3>Leadership Labs</h3>
        <p>Real-world challenges that build decision-making, teamwork and communication skills.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="study.svg" alt="icon"/>
        <h3>Academic Boost</h3>
        <p>Targeted tutoring and study strategies that turn struggle into success.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="community.svg" alt="icon"/>
        <h3>Community Impact</h3>
        <p>Service-learning projects that connect classroom knowledge to community needs.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact">
    <h2>Get Started</h2>
    <div class="cta">
      <h3>Ready to join us?</h3>
      <p>Contact us today to schedule a free orientation session.</p>
      <a href="mailto:hello@intelligentscholars.com">Enroll Now</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<footer>
  &copy; 2025 Intelligent Scholars Academy. All rights reserved.
</footer>

</body>
</html>
```

How to customize quickly
1. Replace the three .svg images with your own (64 × 64 px PNG/SVG works best).  
   - leadership.svg → a leadership icon  
   - study.svg → a study icon  
   - community.svg → a volunteering icon  
   (Free icon sets: heroicons.com, tabler-icons.io, or undraw.co illustrations for bigger graphics.)

2. Colors: change the CSS variables `--primary` and `--secondary` to match your brand palette.

3. Content: edit the “About Us” paragraph and card descriptions to fit your actual programs.

4. Hosting:  
   - Drag-and-drop the folder onto Netlify or Vercel, or  
   - Enable GitHub Pages in your repository settings.

That’s it—your youth academy now has a clean, modern landing page that works on phones, tablets and desktops.
